name: Nightmare Fan Art
description:
I do not do a lot of fan art, but my nephew is a huge Nightmare before Christmas fan and begged for this one.  LOL.  I thought the #HENHalloween event would be the perfect time to bring it around! #HENHalloween is a community event hosted by @rblbab, @cemo and @brainksy.  

This is a hand drawn artwork using chalk, markers and colored pencils and then edited digitally.
